{"tid":1692884,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「突發第二擊 - 敵退我追」請立即去警謊記者會FB直播，宣傳今晚民間記者會，等藍絲有機會跳出同溫層","createTime":"2019-11-04T09:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:25:32.000Z","uid":47208,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bded88fb7a9f60463f35890c4117a434da70f625","tid":1692884,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<strong>參考第一擊：</strong><br />\n今晚8點，擊民間記者會駁入電視全家食飯睇<br />\n<br />\n「突發」警謊記者會收皮，有天時地利，今晚要幫手推民間記者會，要拎埋人和<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692766\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692766</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>敵退我追，第二擊： 讓藍絲跳出同溫層</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警謊記者會改為網上直播，<br />\n係個超好既渠道向藍絲宣傳民間記者會既存在<br />\n<br />\n我想邀請手足幫手去警謊FB留言，<br />\n呼籲所有人今晚8點睇民記，<br />\n但為避免推高警謊記者會人數，<br />\n入去回覆完就好走<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/videos/2656165037779058/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2Fvideos%2F2656165037779058%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=db05377f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/videos/2656165037779058/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTemplate: <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">第二十三次民間記者會<br />\n<br />\n主題：魔警濫權，人神共憤；公僕同僚，恥與為伍<br />\n日期：2019年11月4日（星期一）<br />\n時間：晚上8:00<br />\n<br />\n大家可於以下頻道收看：</span><br />\n*********<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n*自已係下面copy 其中一條link，最好不同，唔好比人覺得洗版<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家可於以下或其他頻道收看直播：<br />\n基進報導：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fradicalhk&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=5bf0c16d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk</